Class AbstractDataSeries<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • hivis.data.DataSetDefault

    DataSeries<V>, DataSet, Iterable<V>

extends DataSetDefault
implements DataSeries<V>

      • toUnitRange

        public DataSeries<Double> toUnitRange()
        Description copied from interface: DataSeries
        Create a view of this series containing the values in this series scaled to the unit range [0, 1]. Equivalent to this.subtract(this.minValue()).divide(this.maxValue() - this.minValue()).asDouble(), however the values in the view will be updated when the vales in the series change.
        Specified by:
        toUnitRange in interface DataSeries<V>
